  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/3599",
  "title": "chore(storybook): add support for playgrounds",
  "body": "This adds supports for different playgrounds in the Storybook so that we can use other datasets than `instant_search`.\r\n\r\nIt's necessary for writing stories about Query Rules.\r\n\r\n## Files updates\r\n\r\n- Renamed\r\n  - `.storybook/decorators.js` → `.storybook/decorators.ts`\r\n- Edited\r\n  - `.storybook/decorators.ts`: added support for playgrounds\r\n- Added\r\n  - `.storybook/playgrounds/movies.ts`\r\n\r\n## Usage\r\n\r\n```js\r\nimport moviesPlayground from '../.storybook/playgrounds/movies';\r\n\r\nstoriesOf('MyStory', module).add(\r\n  'default',\r\n  withHits(\r\n    ({ search, container, instantsearch }) => {\r\n      // ...\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      appId: '',\r\n      apiKey: '',\r\n      indexName: '',\r\n      playground: moviesPlayground, // this is taken into account\r\n    }\r\n  )\r\n);\r\n\r\n```",
  "created_at": "2019-03-12T16:43:05Z",
